data.title: 317 392 SILVER BERRY RD NW, Edmonton, Alberta, T6T0H1 Edmonton AB CA
data.meta_description:
Spacious 2 Bedroom open concept Condo in Silverberry. This condo comes with 1 Heated Underground Parking Stall & Storage. This condo has gym and underground carwash. Unit has laundry room with storage, spacious kitchen, living and dining room area. The kitchen features plenty of counter and cabinet space. Large Master Suite with walk in closet and full ensuite. Second full good size bedroom. Spacious open concept living room with patio door that opens up to large private balcony. This location is in close proximity to schools, park, walking trails, public transport, Recreation center with easy access to Anthony Henday and Whitemud. (id:1937)
